Charter Oak Partners, a Connecticutinvestment partnership, said it raised its stake in FacetEnterprises Inc to 480,000 shares, or 9.6 pct of the totaloutstanding common stock, from 300,000 shares, or 6.0 pct.    In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission,Charter Oak said it bought 180,000 Facet common shares on June12 at 18.25 dlrs each. Reuter&#3;